author: Jon Carroll
title: Here today, gone already: It’s ‘Pop-Up Magazine’!
text: So it all started when I wrote a mash note to Douglas McGray, the editor of California Sunday magazine, which arrives with your newspaper every month but is not produced by your newspaper. California Sunday is an adventure in journalism, not so different from (say) the New York Times Magazine, but also very different.
